honline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25304,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/10\/22\/ahmad-follow-sunnah\/","url_meta":{"origin":4098,"position":2},"title":"Ahmad on Sunnah: Do not blindly follow me, follow Hadith","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 22, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abdul Barr reported: Imam Ahmad ibn Hanbal, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cAl-Awza\u2019i had opinions, Malik had opinions, Sufyan al-Thawri had opinions. Each of them had opinions, and it is all the same to me. Indeed, the proof is only in the narrations.\u201d In another narration, Imam\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38862,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/02\/21\/imam-ahmad-dua-rulers\/","url_meta":{"origin":4098,"position":3},"title":"Ahmad on Rulers: Supplication for guidance of Caliphs and Imams","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 21, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Bakr al-Marrudhi reported: I heard Ahmad ibn Hanbal, may Allah have mercy on him, mentioning the Caliph al-Mutawakkil and he said, \u201cIndeed, I pray for his righteousness and well-being.\u201d Source: al-Sunnah li-Abi\u0304 Bakr al-Khalla\u0304l 16 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u200c\u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0628\u064e\u0643\u0652\u0631\u064d \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064f\u0651\u0648\u0630\u0650\u064a\u064f\u0651 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0633\u064e\u0645\u0650\u0639\u0652\u062a\u064f \u0623\u064e\u062d\u0652\u0645\u064e\u062f\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u064e \u062d\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0628\u064e\u0644\u064d \u0631\u064e\u062d\u065